Pi;;85;;88;;R;;Numbers whiz Max Cohen (Sean Gullette) is stunted by psychological delusions of paranoia and debilitating headaches. He lives in a messy Chinatown apartment, where he tinkers with equations and his homemade, super-advanced computer. One day, however, Cohen encounters a mysterious number. Soon after reporting his discovery to his mentor (Mark Margolis) and to a religious friend (Ben Shenkman), he finds himself the target of ill-intentioned Wall Street agents bent on using the number for profit.;;Drama;;Darren Aronofsky;;1998;;Sean Gullette,Mark Margolis,Ben Shenkman,Pamela Hart,Steve Pearlman,Samia Shoaib,Lauren Fox,Ajay Naidu,Tom Tumminello,Espher Lao Nieves;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pi